$ Stellarium API: StelMovementMgr.zoomTo

`StelMovementMgr.zoomTo` changes the *field of view*.

code {
StelMovementMgr.zoomTo(
  100, // Angle of field of view
    0  // Duration for zoom to take place
);
code }

gh|about-Stellarium|/API/StelMovementMgr/zoomTo.ssc||

sa:

  The maximum *fov* (field of view) can be set with → Wissenschaft/Astronomie/tools/Stellarium/script/API/StelMovementMgr/setMaxFov[`StelMovementMgr.setMaxFov(…)`]

  The → Wissenschaft/Astronomie/tools/Stellarium#stellarium-shortcut[keyboard shortcuts] to change the zoom (Field of view, FOV) seems to be `ctrl-alt-0` … `ctrl-alt-9`.

  → Wissenschaft/Astronomie/tools/Stellarium/script/API
